videos.headline: USC opens scoring with 82-yard punt return TD
videos.description: Tyler Vaughns makes several defenders miss as he takes the punt 82 yards to the house for an early USC touchdown.

videos.headline: Arizona St. QB lets one rip for 44-yard touchdown.
videos.description: Arizona State quarterback Manny Wilkins places a perfect pass downfield to N'Keal Harry for a 44-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Sun Devils RB breaks multiple tackles for 49-yard TD
videos.description: Sun Devils running back Eno Benjamin finds a hole and takes it to the house for a 49-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Jones Jr. cuts through traffic for 9-yard touchdown
videos.description: Jones Jr. cuts through traffic for 9-yard touchdown

videos.headline: USC trick play leads to 36-yard touchdown
videos.description: USC WR Velus Jones Jr. delivers a perfect pass to Michael Pittman Jr. for a 36-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: N'Keal Harry follows blocks for 92-yard punt return TD
videos.description: Arizona State sets up a perfect blocking pattern for WR N'Keal Harry and takes it to the house for a 92-yard punt return TD.

videos.headline: ASU QB calls his own number for 45-yard touchdown
videos.description: Arizona State quarterback Manny Wilkins fakes the handoff and runs it in for a 45-yard touchdown increasing ASU's lead to 38-28.
